
.page
  %header.site-header
    .logo
      %img{ src: "/logo.png", alt: "Socks" }
  %main
    %section.intro
      %h2 Find the sock that matches you
      %p
        Socks is a lighthearted dating app built around a simple idea:
        every sock is better with a good match. Browse, connect, and see
        where your next pairing leads.

    %section.actions
      %a.button.primary{ href: "/signup" } Sign up
      %a.button.secondary{ href: "/login" } Log in
  %footer.site-footer
    %p
      An application built by Grace College students. No missing socks were harmed.
